            <title>[HADOOP-17360] Log the remote address for authentication success</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-17360</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;IPC server logs &quot;Authentication successful for USER&quot;. &lt;br/&gt;
